name: Qt
description:
Provides integration for Qt projects using CMake:
  • Code assistance for Qt keywords like signals, slots, and Q_OBJECT.
  • Automatic handling of generated sources like MOC, UIC, and RCC files.
  • Run/debug configurations for Qt applications.
  • Qt renderers support in the CLion debugger.
  • QtCreator keymap.
This plugin is endorsed but not maintained by the Qt Group.
